## 3-Layer Architecture Overview
As documented in `DEMODEPLOYMENT.md`, the system is structured into 3 integrated layers:

| Layer | URL | What It Is |
|-------|-----|-----------|
| **Layer 1 (Frontend)** | http://localhost:3000 | Serves BOTH the Public Library Webpage (`/`) and the Admin Panel (`/admin`) via React Router. |
| **Layer 2 (Backend)** | http://localhost:8000/api | Django REST API |
| **Layer 3 (Database)**| localhost:5432 | PostgreSQL (internal network, accessible via DBeaver/pgAdmin) |

